title: Fossil Hybrid Smart Watch - Q Accomplice Stainless Steel
feature: Looks like a watch, acts like a smartwatch—these no-charge hybrid smartwatches feature built-in activity tracking, filtered notifications and multiple time zones
Snap a photo, ring your phone, control your music and more with the customizable link button
Track your everyday accomplishments including steps, distance, and calories burned and monitor your sleep duration and quality

When a notification or alert arrives for an important text, email or app update, a gentle buzz lets you know right away. This wrist essential is always on, always connected with a battery life up to six months and automatically syncs to your phone
Fit your style with interchangable straps - compatible with all Fossil brand 16mm straps. Compatibility: Android OS 5.0+, iPhone 5/iOS 9.0+, Smartphone App
description: Slim, smart and even more customizable, our Q Accomplice hybrid looks like a watch, but acts like a smartwatch.
